---
title: Sage and Brown Butter Pork Chops with Roasted Butternut Squash and Charred Broccolini
description: Sage adds earthy depth to honeyed squash and juicy pork chops in this Instagram-worthy dish. Roasting the broccolini helps develop crispy edges and a nutty flavour - try it with regular broccoli, too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sage-and-brown-butter-pork-chops-2e7f4d18.jpg
